issue.title: Things I stumbled on
issue.body:
Hey great project, just want to publish some notes on what I stumbled against:


  1. There's a few deprecation notices for S3-apis in terraform
  2. The output doesn't tell you the valheim address
  3. xbox game pass support obviously not detailed

I'm working through these now, will update as I fix.

issue.title: Adds classes for img2img and txt2img
issue.body:
These classes use functions and code from scripts/txt2img.py and scripts/img2img.py

- The `main` function from each of those scripts was copied to these classes, original script code remains intact
- **Low impact:** The new classes are not an immediate replacement for the scripts, but this allows the scripts to be deprecated so that the rest of the code can migrate to a class-based architecture if desired.

Using classes allows

- The ability to extend and overwrite some of the logic embeded in the scripts files
- Easier testing
- Easier to write plugins

pull_request.title: Add fprefix command argument
pull_request.body:
Add fprefix command argument. Permits an arbitrarily configured "Filename PREFIX".

Ex: python scripts/txt2img.py --plms --n_iter 5 --n_samples 1 --skip_grid --fprefix 2022.09.10-0312- --prompt "a photograph of an astronaut riding a horse" Results in sample filenames as "2022.09.10-0312-00128.png", and etc.

I found use for this argument. Figured I'd contribute and maybe someone else will also find this useful.
